{"tid":337670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★本港逾24.3萬獨居女性 較15年前增逾91%","createTime":"2017-07-27T13:31:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-28T11:44:59.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f44f36b1b5cea438e5c30de716648c2cf3b55ef5","tid":337670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:31:36.000Z","msg":"政府統計處今日公佈《香港的女性及男性─主要統計數字》，本港去年有超過24.3萬名獨居女性，較2001年激增逾91%；獨居男性則逾21.5萬，增幅也有33%。此外，男女性平均預期壽命也創新高，男性為81.3歲，女性則87.3歲。<br />\n<br />\n本港去年女性人口超過364萬，男性逾337萬，分別較2011年增多19.26萬及7.24萬。男女比例越趨失衡，由2006年每千名女性對971名男性，進一步拉闊至去年每千名女性對925名男性。而勞動人口中的男女性比例，也逐漸拉近，差不多打成平手。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170727/57009157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170727%2F57009157&d=LzsLq5pDfCYS%2FRqxTYrJTwCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=c0b30c32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170727%2F57009157&h=6924ecc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170727/57009157</a>"},{"pid":"c6a46a472cb9f04b44631fd1dc8acdb63f74b05c","tid":337670,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:31:43.000Z","msg":"獨居男性則逾21.5萬"},{"pid":"e8269c915f2c1b52100c60f61fbb567c7c63ea32","tid":337670,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:37:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"97e786be75ac08f604338f2270cd433f524d54af","tid":337670,"uid":128210,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T13:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寧願獨居都唔揀毒撚</blockquote><br />\n比著你都唔會選<br />\n<br />\n利申，毒撚"},{"pid":"a9521fcfd012d8841061e7b6a310fde71951ab4f","tid":337670,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T14:18:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f9af9848d9ffe22f5a4a8c3196344e97aac7f7a","tid":337670,"u